data.description:
Looking for a townhome within easy reach of Denver but where the smell of fresh pine still floats in your window? Welcome to Aspen Meadows. This community of townhomes, with its beautiful stacked stone and siding aesthetic, has everything you need right at your fingertips, with all the shopping, restaurants, schools, and parks within about ten minutes.
It’s plain to see that this place has been well-maintained with lots of care and love!
The sunshine will follow you as you step inside, washing the living room with its western light through the large front window. The warm, yet light and airy feel of the home will capture you right away; this was created to be a happy place. The eye-catching wood flooring and abundance of windows ensure that this charm is here to stay. 
Check out the fantastic floor plan, which flows seamlessly from room to room, while still offering privacy and space for all. The kitchen has the perfect amount of lighting and features all stainless steel appliances, tile countertops, and a full pantry. That wonderful wood flooring continues into your dining room, where you’ll also find the sliding glass door, leading to your back balcony. Can’t you see yourself heading out there to greet the mornings? 
 The staircases here are both switchbacks for the ease and safety of those younger members of the family. The home has three bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms: plenty of room for everyone! The primary bedroom has its own ensuite bathroom with a lovely vanity, double sinks, and a shower/tub. The other two bedrooms are warm and bright, one of which has its closet transformed into a reading nook! You’ll have a full, two-car garage and plenty of parking space, not to mention the perks of no lawn maintenance. 
This townhouse is sure to delight and check every box on your must-have home list.
And it’s waiting to be yours. Give me a call to schedule your showing today!
